  "stem": "<p>In the <em>xy</em>-plane, the graphs of <math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></math> and <math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math> intersect at two points. Which of the following is one of those points?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p>(-2, 5)</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
      "content": "<p>(0, 5)</p>"
