  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. Setting the expressions equal gives <math><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>, so <math><mfenced open=\"|\" close=\"|\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></math>. Thus <em>x</em> - 1 = 3 or <em>x</em> - 1 = -3, giving <em>x</em> = 4 or <em>x</em> = -2. Of the choices, (-2, 5) is given.</p><p>Choices B, C, and D are incorrect.</p>",
